182
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,320
in this world.

183
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:28,240
It's a deal then.

184
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,360
Whether it's this life

185
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:32,120
or the next,

186
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,799
